伊芙琳护士！伊芙琳护士！
Nurse Evelyn! Nurse Evelyn!

4
00:04:15,050 --> 00:04:17,810
我有讯息要跟你说，用英文写的！
I have a message for you. In English!

5
00:04:35,370 --> 00:04:37,600
就是这个
And here we go.

6
00:04:37,670 --> 00:04:42,080
看看，这是上个月以来所有病人的名单
Now, look, here's the list of all the patients we've had in the ward in the last month.

7
00:04:49,380 --> 00:04:50,610
谢谢，护士
Thank you, Nurse.

8
00:05:58,090 --> 00:06:00,950
- 你是亚历珊卓？ - 是的
- You're Alexandria?  - Yes.

9
00:06:01,020 --> 00:06:05,250
你的纸条飞进来，掉在我的膝部
Your note came in, and landed on my lap.

10
00:06:05,330 --> 00:06:07,560
完全看不懂，是胡乱涂鸦还是什么的
Couldn't even understand it. It's written in gibberish or something.

11
00:06:07,630 --> 00:06:12,360
你看不懂，对吗！你看不懂，那不是写给你的
You didn't understand it, didn't you, didn't understand it, it's not for you.

12
00:06:16,740 --> 00:06:18,230
我叫罗依
My name's Roy.

13
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:22,880
- 你是怎么伤了手臂的？ - 我跌了下来
- How'd you hurt your arm?  - I fell.

14
00:06:24,150 --> 00:06:25,130
我也是
Me too.

15
00:06:25,210 --> 00:06:27,080
当时我在采橘子
I was picking oranges.

16
00:06:29,480 --> 00:06:30,850
是那样吗？
Is that so?

17
00:06:33,390 --> 00:06:35,360
那你要如何上厕所？
How do you go to the potty?

18
00:06:35,420 --> 00:06:38,480
我不用去，他们让我在这里上
I don't. They let me go right here.

19
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:41,290
- 在床上？ - 是呀！是真的
- In bed?  - Yeah, it's true.

20
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,950
我不相信
I don't believe.

21
00:06:44,670 --> 00:06:47,100
嘿！亚历珊卓
Hey, Alexandria.

22
00:06:47,170 --> 00:06:50,730
嘿！你知道你的名字是根据阿历山大大帝的名字取的？
Hey, do you know you're named after Alexander the Great

23
00:06:50,810 --> 00:06:53,600
他是史上最伟大的战士喔！
who was the greatest warrior who ever lived?

24
00:06:53,670 --> 00:06:57,440
是的，我的纸条不是随便涂鸦，那是英文！
Yes. And my note is not in gibberish. It's in English!

25
00:06:57,510 --> 00:06:59,980
嘿！我可以看到你，快过来这
Hey, I can see you. Come on out here.

26
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:03,780
我看见你躲在那
I can see you hiding.

27
00:07:05,150 --> 00:07:06,450
亚历珊卓
Alexandria.

28
00:07:10,660 --> 00:07:13,990
嘿！你知道亚历山大也在等待讯息吗？
Hey, did you know he was also looking for a message?

29
00:07:17,970 --> 00:07:19,400
他迷路了
He was lost.

30
00:07:22,240 --> 00:07:26,700
几乎要死了，跟他的大军走散了
He almost died, separated from his army.

31
00:07:28,010 --> 00:07:31,410
- 他收到讯息了吗？ - 什么？
- Did he find the message?  - What?

32
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:35,140
后来他有收到讯息吗？亚历山大大帝
Did she find the message? Alexandria the Great.

33
00:07:35,220 --> 00:07:37,950
好好，我告诉你，你过来
All right, right, I'll tell you, just come in here.

34
00:07:39,950 --> 00:07:42,350
过来，抓把椅子过来坐下
Now, come on, grab that chair right there.

35
00:07:45,260 --> 00:07:47,890
好的，别弄断了另一条手臂
All right, don't break your other arm.

36
00:07:53,130 --> 00:07:55,260
- 谢谢  - 不客气
- Thank you.  - You're welcome.

37
00:08:00,580 --> 00:08:03,410
- 盒子里有什么？ - 我喜欢的东西
- What's in your box?  - Things I like.

38
00:08:05,450 --> 00:08:08,710
- 是你偷的吗？ - 不
- Things you stole?  - No.

39
00:08:10,280 --> 00:08:11,680
是照片
A photo.

40
00:08:13,120 --> 00:08:15,320
你那来的大象？
Where'd you get the elephant?

41
00:08:16,420 --> 00:08:18,790
我朋友送的
My friend gave it to me at work.

42
00:08:21,130 --> 00:08:22,790
他是印度人
He's from India.

43
00:08:23,870 --> 00:08:28,230
看，这是我的马
Look, this is my horse

44
00:08:30,140 --> 00:08:33,200
- 这是我的父亲  - 是吗？
- and this is my father.  - Yeah?

45
00:08:34,580 --> 00:08:37,700
他的门牙中间有缝隙，这应该是你们家族的特征
He's got the same gap in his teeth, must run in the family.

46
00:08:37,780 --> 00:08:40,440
- 是呀！这是我家  - 是吗？
- Yeah, and here is my house.  - Oh, yeah?

47
00:08:40,520 --> 00:08:43,040
- 这曾经是我家  - 怎么了？
- It was my house.  - What happened?

48
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:45,680
- 他们烧了它  - 谁？
- They burn it.  - Who burned it?

49
00:08:46,650 --> 00:08:48,090
愤怒的人们
Angry people.

50
00:08:49,990 --> 00:08:51,520
听到这我很难过
I'm sorry to hear that.

51
00:08:52,330 --> 00:08:54,620
我说，听到这我很难过
I said, I'm sorry to hear that.

52
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:56,790
愤怒的人们
Angry people.

53
00:08:56,860 --> 00:08:59,660
是呀！我知道，听到你的房子被烧了我很难过
Yeah, I know, I'm just sorry that your house got burned.

54
00:08:59,730 --> 00:09:01,960
为何阿历山大
Why did Alexander

55
00:09:02,040 --> 00:09:07,130
没有从建筑物里面骑马出来？
didn't go from that buildings on his horse?

56
00:09:08,210 --> 00:09:10,540
- 若是他迷路了…  - 什么？
- If him was lost...  - What?

57
00:09:10,610 --> 00:09:19,740
为何阿历山大不从房里面骑马出来？
Why did Alexander didn't go from that middle of the buildings from that buildings on his horse?

58
00:09:21,060 --> 00:09:22,390
嗯…
Well...

59
00:09:24,530 --> 00:09:30,560
首先，他没有马，因为他的马在战争中死了
First of all, he didn't have a horse because his horse was killed in a battle.

60
00:09:33,330 --> 00:09:36,130
况且，他也不是在任何房子里
And he wasn't in the middle of any old buildings.

61
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:42,570
而是在广大沙漠中迷路了，四周尽是橙黄色的沙子
He was lost in the middle of a vast desert, full of orange sand

62
00:09:42,640 --> 00:09:44,670
身边只有几个随从
with only a handful of men

63
00:09:46,950 --> 00:09:49,420
但是他们连一滴水也没有
but they didn't have any water.

64
00:10:12,210 --> 00:10:13,300
看！
Look!

65
00:10:38,970 --> 00:10:42,300
“大人，一切希望都没了
"My Lord, all hope is lost.

66
00:10:42,370 --> 00:10:46,240
“似乎您的大军终将被征服
"It seems your mighty army shall finally be conquered.

67
00:10:46,310 --> 00:10:51,640
“不是被波私人，而是被缺水所打败
"Not by the Persians, but by our own greed and gluttony for water.

68
00:10:51,710 --> 00:10:54,700
“这顶头盔，就是我们仅能提供的
"This helmet contains our last supply.

69
00:10:56,220 --> 00:10:59,520
“喔！大王，我相信你的智慧将会让我们得救”
"Oh, King, I believe your wisdom shall save us all."

70
00:11:09,130 --> 00:11:10,460
- 为什么？ - 为什么？
- Why?  - Why?

71
00:11:10,530 --> 00:11:11,620
什么？
What?

72
00:11:13,030 --> 00:11:14,130
为什么？
Why?

73
00:11:15,940 --> 00:11:19,770
因为水不够所有人喝
Well, because there wasn't enough water for all of them

74
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:22,370
而且那就是阿历山大大帝做事的方法
and it was Alexander the Great's way

75
00:11:22,440 --> 00:11:25,000
像他的军队显示他们一切平等…
of showing his army that they were all equal...

76
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:26,910
真是蠢啊
It's stupid.

77
00:11:26,980 --> 00:11:28,350
那你会怎样做比较好？
What would you do better?

78
00:11:28,420 --> 00:11:30,980
阿历山大为什么把水倒掉
Was Alexander throw the water

79
00:11:31,050 --> 00:11:35,820
而不是给每个人都喝一小口呢
instead to give every soldier a little bit.

80
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:45,530
嘿！你何不明天再来，我再跟你说另个故事
Hey, why don't you come back tomorrow and I'm going to tell you a different story.

81
00:11:45,600 --> 00:11:49,430
史诗般的爱情与复仇故事
An epic tale of love and revenge.

82
00:11:49,500 --> 00:11:51,800
- 你知道“史诗般”是什么意思吗？ - 不知道
- You know what "epic" means?  - No.

83
00:11:51,870 --> 00:11:54,100
我这里仍然闷闷的，好像连…
I still got this tightness here. It's like I can't even...

84
00:11:54,180 --> 00:11:57,510
那表示是个很长的故事，而且发生在印度
It means a really long story, and it's set in India.

85
00:11:57,580 --> 00:11:58,980
…好像胸口有只大象那样沉重
...the elephant sitting on my chest.

86
00:11:59,050 --> 00:12:00,980
- 你将会很快好转的  - 好的，继续
- You should be fully recovered.  - All right, go on.

87
00:12:01,050 --> 00:12:02,980
- 我要你帮我检查  - 你明天会在来吗？
- I want you to examine me.  - Will you come back tomorrow?

88
00:12:03,050 --> 00:12:05,810
我觉得不太好
You personally. I'm not very well.

89
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:15,660
肿胀似乎消了点
The swelling seems down.

90
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:19,820
我知道那很痛
I know how much it hurts.

91
00:12:22,700 --> 00:12:25,140
幽默一下
A sense of humor.

92
00:12:25,210 --> 00:12:29,470
几周后疼痛会消失，然后在做一次手术
In the next couple of weeks the pain should abate, then one more operation.

93
00:12:29,540 --> 00:12:31,310
跟上次一样吗？
Like the last one?

94
00:12:31,380 --> 00:12:34,370
这需要你的努力，知道吗？
This is going to take some effort on your part, too, you know that?

95
00:12:34,450 --> 00:12:35,570
看见没？
See?

96
00:13:23,430 --> 00:13:24,950
过来
Come on, then.

97
00:13:46,620 --> 00:13:48,750
- 午餐前回来  - 好的
- Be back before lunch.  - Okay.

98
00:14:07,410 --> 00:14:09,930
亚历珊卓，离开那冰块
Alexandria, get away from that ice.

99
00:14:10,010 --> 00:14:13,000
我看到你舔冰块，你会生病的
I see you licking that ice, you're gonna get sick.

100
00:14:13,080 --> 00:14:15,050
去别地方玩！
I want you to go play, go!

101
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:18,240
下次我会将你的舌头黏在冰块上将你载走
Next time, I'll glue your lips to this and carry you away.

102
00:14:24,790 --> 00:14:27,320
只有马死了你要觉得幸运了
You're lucky it was just a horse that got killed.

103
00:14:27,390 --> 00:14:31,420
我是说，从铁道桥上跳下来，无疑是自杀
I mean, jumping off a train bridge was suicide, too.

104
00:14:31,500 --> 00:14:33,560
若是你想要上她印象深刻…
And if you were trying to impress her...

105
00:14:34,540 --> 00:14:37,600
辛克莱比较吸引她
Sinclair already did a better job.

106
00:14:37,670 --> 00:14:39,430
你知道，那男演员
You know, the actor,

107
00:14:41,110 --> 00:14:43,630
- 男主角  - 我知道他是谁
- the leading man.  - I know who he is.

108
00:14:45,010 --> 00:14:47,980
只有熬过困难才会有拨云见日的一天，那是一定的
Every cloud has a silver lining, that's for sure.

109
00:14:48,050 --> 00:14:49,110
拿另外一张牌
Take another card.

110
00:14:49,180 --> 00:14:51,780
- 在我发生意外前…  - 那是红心Q
- You know, before my accident...  - That is the Queen of Hearts.

111
00:14:51,850 --> 00:14:53,180
…事事顺利
...nothing was happening for me.

112
00:14:53,250 --> 00:14:56,880
现在我的腿被粗鲁的人砍伤
Now I've had my leg hacked off by savages,

113
00:14:56,960 --> 00:15:00,720
被马车压过，然后被锯掉
mangled by chariots, sawed off by lumberjacks.

114
00:15:00,790 --> 00:15:04,920
嗯，还被一只鱼叉穿过，我一直在工作
Hell, I've even had a harpoon through it. I'm working all the time.

115
00:15:09,600 --> 00:15:11,800
这是黑桃二
That is the two of spades.

116
00:15:11,870 --> 00:15:14,840
- 片场正想要补偿你  - 抱歉，沙巴提尼先生
- The studio is just trying to do right by you.  - Excuse me, Mr. Sabatini.

117
00:15:14,910 --> 00:15:17,040
钱就收下吧
Take the money.

118
00:15:17,110 --> 00:15:20,410
无论如何，娱乐圈不适合你，罗依
Anyway, gags are not for you, Roy.

119
00:15:20,480 --> 00:15:21,780
你该是个读书人
You're a college man.

120
00:15:21,850 --> 00:15:22,870
我不是
Wasn't me.

121
00:15:22,950 --> 00:15:24,650
一个瘸子的忠告…
One cripple to another...

122
00:15:26,420 --> 00:15:28,050
我没有朝你丢橘子
I didn't throw orange at you.

123
00:15:28,120 --> 00:15:30,220
…没有女人值得为她自杀
...no woman is worth suicide.

124
00:15:31,630 --> 00:15:33,650
想要跟那人一样当明星，看在老天的分上
Like the guy's a movie star, for chrissake.

125
00:15:49,410 --> 00:15:51,670
你的朋友是个海盗吗？
Was your friend a pirate?

126
00:15:54,920 --> 00:15:57,150
你的朋友是个海盗吗？
Was your friend a pirate?

127
00:15:58,820 --> 00:16:00,220
有时候是
Sometimes.

128
00:16:01,820 --> 00:16:05,090
他当海盗才伤了脚？
Is that how he hurt his leg?

129
00:16:05,160 --> 00:16:09,260
不，他…他为电影做特技
No, he... He does tricks for pictures.

130
00:16:09,330 --> 00:16:12,130
就是电影啊
You know, flickers.

131
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:14,100
动画片
Moving pictures.

132
00:16:15,070 --> 00:16:18,160
- 我没看过电影  - 你也没错过什么啦
- I never seen one.  - You're not missing much.

133
00:16:19,410 --> 00:16:22,030
你也跟你朋友做一样的工作吗？
Is that what you do, like your friend?

134
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:25,280
只做了一次
Just once.

135
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:31,420
现在可以跟我说故事了吗？
Will you tell me the story now?

136
00:16:32,490 --> 00:16:35,010
- 什么故事？ - 史诗故事啊
- What story?  - The epic.

137
00:16:38,860 --> 00:16:40,220
好吧
All right.

138
00:16:42,630 --> 00:16:44,650
好，闭上眼睛
All right, close your eyes.

139
00:16:47,470 --> 00:16:49,060
你看到什么？
What do you see?

140
00:16:50,540 --> 00:16:51,770
什么都没有
Nothing.

141
00:16:54,610 --> 00:16:55,910
柔一柔
Rub them.

142
00:16:57,680 --> 00:16:59,410
看到星星没有？
Can you see the stars?

143
00:17:00,880 --> 00:17:02,180
是的
Yes.

144
00:17:02,920 --> 00:17:05,510
那是一个多星的夜晚
It was a starry night.

145
00:17:05,590 --> 00:17:10,320
四个人在一个小岛上焦急地等着
Four men waited impatiently on a small island

146
00:17:10,390 --> 00:17:13,380
四周海水平静无声
surrounded by a calm sea.

147
00:17:13,460 --> 00:17:16,660
但是这平静是假的
But that calmness was deceptive.

148
00:17:21,600 --> 00:17:23,830
因为在那时候
For at that moment

149
00:17:23,900 --> 00:17:28,340
有个腿绑绷带的印度人，朝向他们游了过来
an Indian with a bandaged thigh swam towards them.

150
00:17:35,250 --> 00:17:36,810
告诉我，印度人
Tell me, Indian.

151
00:17:37,790 --> 00:17:39,280
是真的吗？
Is it true?

152
00:17:42,520 --> 00:17:46,480
路易奇，什么是真的？
Luigi, is what true?

153
00:17:47,590 --> 00:17:51,660
欧迪亚斯总督明天将会将你的孪生哥哥处死
Governor Odious will execute your twin brother tomorrow morning.

154
00:17:52,900 --> 00:17:54,630
我可怜的哥哥
My poor brother.

155
00:18:00,840 --> 00:18:03,780
现在他们有五个人
In all, there were five of them.

156
00:18:03,840 --> 00:18:06,510
他们只有一个共通点
They had only one thing in common,

157
00:18:06,580 --> 00:18:09,520
憎恨欧迪亚斯总督
a hatred of Governor Odious.

158
00:18:11,120 --> 00:18:15,820
第一个人以前是个奴隶，奥塔・班加
The first was an ex-slave, Otta Benga.

159
00:18:23,100 --> 00:18:27,060
他与他哥哥生而为奴隶
He and his brother were born into slavery

160
00:18:27,130 --> 00:18:31,260
工作只是为了填满邪恶欧迪亚斯总督的金库而已
only to fill the coffers of the evil Governor Odious.

161
00:18:33,370 --> 00:18:37,210
有天他正在田里做苦力…
One day while toiling in the fields...

162
00:18:50,590 --> 00:18:55,320
因为哥哥的死伤心至极，他释放了其他奴隶
Heartbroken at his brother's death, he freed the slaves

163
00:18:55,400 --> 00:18:59,800
发誓他要亲自杀死欧迪亚斯总督
and swore that he would be responsible for Governor Odious's death.

164
00:19:03,500 --> 00:19:04,900
我喜欢他
I like him.

165
00:19:04,970 --> 00:19:08,270
然后是印度人
Then, there was the Indian,

166
00:19:08,340 --> 00:19:12,180
当他紧张时，总是会拨弄眉毛
who, whenever anxious, always stroked his brow.

167
00:19:16,150 --> 00:19:23,110
印度人原本要娶世界上最美的女人
The Indian was supposedly married to the most beautiful squaw in the world

168
00:19:23,190 --> 00:19:25,850
但是没人见过这女人
yet nobody had seen her.

169
00:19:25,930 --> 00:19:30,360
为了证实，他伪装成q疯病患者
To verify this, Odious disguised himself as a leper

170
00:19:30,430 --> 00:19:34,420
他见到她的倒影时，立刻为她神魂颠倒
but when he saw her reflection, he was smitten.

171
