什么？
What?

343
00:38:40,910 --> 00:38:44,680
好，那你要我…那你要我怎么说话？
Okay, how do you want me... How do you want him to speak?

344
00:38:44,750 --> 00:38:46,580
我想到我们一起的快乐时光
I think of all the joys we had.

345
00:38:46,650 --> 00:38:48,880
正常的说话，像你一样
Normal, like you.

346
00:38:48,950 --> 00:38:51,550
我没有来得及救你，因为当时我虚弱
I could've saved you, but I was weak.

347
00:38:53,490 --> 00:38:57,050
我的悲伤以化成血染的复仇
My grief has gone blood-red with revenge.

348
00:38:59,470 --> 00:39:01,190
我现在已经更强壮
I'm stronger now.

349
00:39:03,340 --> 00:39:09,570
我会在世上各个角落找寻欧迪亚斯总督的踪迹，然后杀掉他！
I will search the four corners of this Earth, find Governor Odious and joyously kill him!

350
00:39:12,810 --> 00:39:16,010
以蓝侠之名，我在此发誓
By the Blue Bandit's honor, I swear

351
00:39:16,080 --> 00:39:20,210
我会歼灭他，还有他的所爱！
I will annihilate him and everything that he loves!

352
00:39:26,790 --> 00:39:31,530
我会歼灭他！我会歼灭他！
I will destroy him! I will destroy him!

353
00:39:31,600 --> 00:39:34,860
我会歼灭他！歼灭他！
Destroy him! I will destroy him!

354
00:39:40,140 --> 00:39:42,510
还有所有西班牙的东西
And every Spanish thing.

355
00:39:43,810 --> 00:39:45,870
我还以为他是西班牙人
I thought he was Spanish.

356
00:39:46,850 --> 00:39:47,940
不
No.

357
00:39:49,480 --> 00:39:51,350
他是法国人
He was French.

358
00:39:51,420 --> 00:39:53,440
你们跟我同一阵线吗？
Are you with me, bandits?

359
00:40:16,280 --> 00:40:19,900
达尔文！要怎么去找欧迪亚斯总督？
Darwin! Which way to Governor Odious?

360
00:40:21,150 --> 00:40:25,480
我跟他说过，别将地图跟虫子放在一起
I tell him not to put the map with the bugs.

361
00:40:26,820 --> 00:40:28,050
我们迷路了吗？
Are we lost?

362
00:40:28,120 --> 00:40:29,210
抱歉，队长
Sorry, Capitaine.

363
00:40:30,560 --> 00:40:32,390
嘿！不！
Hey! No!

364
00:40:35,390 --> 00:40:38,960
嘿！你不可以吃，那有毒！
Hey! You can't eat it, it's poisonous!

365
00:40:47,440 --> 00:40:49,310
他说什么？
What's he saying?

366
00:40:49,380 --> 00:40:53,740
他说跟着他，可以到青翠葱绿的牧场！
He says we should follow him to greener pastures!

367
00:40:53,810 --> 00:40:57,580
- 什么？ - 他说下面有青翠葱绿的牧场
- What?  - He say it's greener down there.

368
00:40:58,180 --> 00:41:00,710
绿洲？下面？
Green? Down where?

369
00:41:00,790 --> 00:41:01,880
我不知道
I don't know.

370
00:41:01,950 --> 00:41:04,120
青翠葱绿的牧场！
To greener pastures!

371
00:41:04,190 --> 00:41:05,680
慢点！
Slow down!

372
00:41:06,960 --> 00:41:10,950
他肚子里的鸟儿渴望着绿洲！
The birds in his belly crave greener pastures!

373
00:41:11,900 --> 00:41:15,090
嘿！青翠葱绿的牧场
Hey! It is greener down there.

374
00:41:16,200 --> 00:41:17,830
青翠葱绿的牧场
Greener pastures.

375
00:41:19,910 --> 00:41:21,340
慢点！
Slow down!

376
00:41:31,450 --> 00:41:35,750
别跑！越跑毒性发作越快！
Please don't run! The poison works faster if you run!

377
00:41:42,430 --> 00:41:43,760
慢点
Slow down.

378
00:41:54,310 --> 00:41:55,470
那有毒
It's poisonous.

379
00:42:03,920 --> 00:42:05,140
什么？
What?

380
00:43:00,770 --> 00:43:02,500
他在指引我们方向
He's giving us directions.

381
00:43:33,640 --> 00:43:34,660
去！
Go!

382
00:44:28,860 --> 00:44:29,990
奴隶！
Slaves!

383
00:44:42,610 --> 00:44:44,370
欧迪亚斯的旗帜
Odious's flag.

384
00:44:50,550 --> 00:44:52,540
我们要是放那些奴隶
We must free the slaves.

385
00:45:07,500 --> 00:45:10,370
告诉我，亚历珊卓，你会看英文吗？
Tell me, Alexandria, do you read English?

386
00:45:11,070 --> 00:45:15,600
你总是在最美好，
You always stop at the same part when it's very beautiful

387
00:45:16,510 --> 00:45:18,200
最有趣的时候停下来
and interesting.

388
00:45:18,280 --> 00:45:21,440
我想知道你会不会看英文
I just wanted to know if you can read English.

389
00:45:21,510 --> 00:45:22,840
会吗？
Can you?

390
00:45:23,920 --> 00:45:26,480
- 你会看英文吗？ - 是呀！
- Can you read English?  - Yeah.

391
00:45:26,550 --> 00:45:29,180
- 这是什么？ - 纸
- What's this?  - Paper.

392
00:45:29,250 --> 00:45:32,050
不，这是什么？这个
No. What's this? This.

393
00:45:32,120 --> 00:45:36,530
M，o，r，p，h…
M-o-r-p-h...

394
00:45:37,800 --> 00:45:39,660
三
Three.

395
00:45:39,730 --> 00:45:41,560
- 那是什么？ - 三
- What's that?  - Three.

396
00:45:41,630 --> 00:45:43,000
很好
That's good.

397
00:45:46,040 --> 00:45:50,000
我一直睡不好，故事不记得了
I'm having a hard time sleeping and I can't remember that story.

398
00:45:52,850 --> 00:45:55,310
我需要一些药物
I need some pills.

399
00:45:55,380 --> 00:45:59,480
我需要的药物，装在写有这些字的瓶子里面
I need pills in a bottle that has this written on them.

400
00:45:59,550 --> 00:46:02,710
M，o，r，p，h，i，n，三？
M-o-r-p-h-i-n-three?

401
00:46:02,790 --> 00:46:05,720
是的，而且就在大道上
Yes. And it's in the main block.

402
00:46:08,960 --> 00:46:11,290
大街上的房间里
In that room in the main block.

403
00:46:15,270 --> 00:46:16,760
懂吗？
You understand?

404
00:46:16,840 --> 00:46:20,400
- 问问护士长  - 我是以朋友的身份求你
- Ask the head nurse.  - I'm asking you as a friend.

405
00:46:20,470 --> 00:46:23,930
- 但那是偷窃  - 不，若是你需要，就不是偷
- But it's stealing.  - No, it's not. Not if you need it.

406
00:46:26,010 --> 00:46:29,310
那跟从教堂偷面包没有差别
It's no different than stealing bread from a church.

407
00:46:31,780 --> 00:46:34,180
- 我去帮你问他们  - 不
- I'll ask them for you.  - No.

408
00:46:35,890 --> 00:46:37,820
那是同伙的秘密
It's a bandit secret.

409
00:46:39,490 --> 00:46:42,860
我需要那药丸，才能继续说故事，懂吗？
I need the pills to finish the story. Understand?

410
00:46:44,130 --> 00:46:46,120
- 我拿不到…  - 我会去做
- I can't get it...  - I'll do it.

411
00:46:47,370 --> 00:46:48,560
谢谢
Thanks.

412
00:47:00,350 --> 00:47:02,180
你看起来好漂亮
You look beautiful.

413
00:47:04,820 --> 00:47:07,290
你为何在脸颊上擦上红色？
Why do you put red on your cheeks?

414
00:47:07,990 --> 00:47:13,550
因为那会让你看来更漂亮
Because it makes you look pretty

415
00:47:18,000 --> 00:47:20,430
也更健康
and healthy, too.

416
00:47:23,970 --> 00:47:26,300
- 记得，午餐前回来  - 我知道！
- Remember, back before lunch.  - I know!

417
00:47:26,370 --> 00:47:29,070
亚历珊卓，今天没有舔冰块？
Alexandria, no licking the ice today?

418
00:47:29,140 --> 00:47:31,700
没有，谢谢！再见！
No. Thank you! Bye!

419
00:47:43,760 --> 00:47:46,420
也许咬一口，但是一窝蛇？
One bite maybe. But a pit of snakes?

420
00:48:17,000 --> 00:48:19,650
[药房]

421
00:48:30,470 --> 00:48:37,140
M，o，r，p，h，i，n，三，M，o，r，p，h，i-n…
M-o-r-p-h-i-n-three. M-o-r-p-h-i-n...

422
00:48:41,950 --> 00:48:44,110
M，o，r，p，h，i，n…
M-o-r-p-h-i-n...

423
00:49:13,480 --> 00:49:18,880
也许你…我知道，听我的很重要
Maybe you got... I know it's important that you listen to me.

424
00:49:18,950 --> 00:49:20,940
你也该想想你的其他孩子
You've gotta think of your other children.

425
00:49:21,720 --> 00:49:23,810
很抱歉
I'm so sorry.

426
00:49:23,890 --> 00:49:27,660
你该警告其他孩子，有关响尾蛇的声音
You have to warn your other children about the sounds of rattlesnakes.

427
00:49:27,730 --> 00:49:32,560
这不是好时机，这附近到处有蛇窝
This isn't a good time. There are snake pits all over this area.

428
00:49:39,270 --> 00:49:42,900
醒醒！醒醒！快起来，否则他们会砍你
Wake up! Wake up! You better get up or they'll chop you.

429
00:49:42,980 --> 00:49:47,280
快起来！你最好快起来，让他们知道你只是在睡觉
You get up! You better get up and show these people you are sleeping.

430
00:49:47,350 --> 00:49:50,780
你不起来那人会剁了你，快起来！
These men will chop you if you don't get up. Get up!

431
00:49:50,850 --> 00:49:53,320
快起来，不是开玩笑
Get up. This isn't funny.

432
00:49:54,420 --> 00:49:56,750
求你，离开这里
Please, let's leave this place.

433
00:50:09,940 --> 00:50:11,840
来！
Come on. Come on!

434
00:50:18,740 --> 00:50:21,110
我一直都那样做
I do that all the time.

435
00:50:21,180 --> 00:50:26,120
你要做的就是换掉湿的衣服，将他们藏起来直到干了为止
All you have to do is change your clothes and hide the wet ones until they're dry.

436
00:50:29,350 --> 00:50:32,810
你知道我遇到可怕的事情时，我怎么做吗？
You know what I do when something frightens me?

437
00:50:32,890 --> 00:50:34,760
我就说神奇咒语
I say the magic words.

438
00:50:37,000 --> 00:50:41,260
走开，走开，走开，走开
Googly, googly, googly, begone.

439
00:50:45,070 --> 00:50:47,660
我们来一起练习
Let's practice together.

440
00:50:47,740 --> 00:50:49,370
神奇咒语
The magic words.

441
00:50:50,210 --> 00:50:53,270
走开，走开，走开
Googly, googly, googly. Go away.

442
00:51:00,690 --> 00:51:03,810
- 你拿到我要你拿的东西吗？ - 是的
- Did you get what I sent you for?  - Yes.

443
00:51:05,720 --> 00:51:07,590
- 这个  - 是吗？
- This it is.  - Yeah?

444
00:51:09,660 --> 00:51:11,560
里面只有三个
There's only three in here.

445
00:51:11,630 --> 00:51:14,720
- 你叫我拿三个  - 不，我叫你拿一整瓶
- You asked me for three.  - No, I asked you for a full bottle.

446
00:51:14,800 --> 00:51:18,170
- 但，你写的…  - 这瓶子里有满满的吗？
- But, you wrote...  - Was this bottle full of pills?

447
00:51:19,810 --> 00:51:21,770
- 里面有更多药丸吗？ - 是呀！
- Were there more pills in here?  - Yeah.

448
00:51:21,840 --> 00:51:23,100
那你拿去哪了？
What did you do with them?

449
00:51:23,180 --> 00:51:25,800
丢进马桶里面了
I throw them in toilet.

450
00:51:27,410 --> 00:51:30,510
因为你写三个，我才丢掉其他的
But I throw them away because you wrote

451
00:51:30,580 --> 00:51:35,380
m-o-r-p-h-i-n-三
m-o-r-p-h-i-n-three.

452
00:51:38,690 --> 00:51:40,850
这可以帮你入眠吗？
Will they help you sleep?

453
00:51:44,660 --> 00:51:46,130
可以小睡一下
A nap perhaps.

454
00:51:53,040 --> 00:51:54,160
我们要解放奴隶
We must free the slaves.

455
00:51:54,240 --> 00:51:56,230
他们有解放了奴隶吗？
Did they free the slaves?

456
00:53:14,290 --> 00:53:15,910
出来，欧迪亚斯
Come out, Odious.

457
00:53:39,410 --> 00:53:41,070
像只蝴蝶
Just like a butterfly.

458
00:53:47,050 --> 00:53:49,820
为何又戴面具？
Why the mask again?

459
00:53:49,890 --> 00:53:52,720
他不想吓到她
He doesn't want to scare her.

460
00:53:52,790 --> 00:53:57,790
她对他一无所知，但是他却知道她的所有事情
She doesn't know anything about him, but he knew everything about her.

461
00:54:00,000 --> 00:54:03,090
眼睛的颜色
The color of her eyes.

462
00:54:04,670 --> 00:54:05,660
棕色
Brown.

463
00:54:06,570 --> 00:54:09,130
她最爱的食物
Her favorite food.

464
00:54:09,210 --> 00:54:10,500
橘子？
Orange?

465
00:54:10,580 --> 00:54:12,670
她最喜欢的书
Her favorite book.

466
00:54:12,740 --> 00:54:13,900
圣经
Bible.

467
00:54:15,010 --> 00:54:18,070
各位，她是我的
Boys, she's mine.

468
00:54:22,590 --> 00:54:24,250
- 炸弹怎么了？ - 什么？
- What about the bomb?  - What?

469
00:54:24,320 --> 00:54:25,580
炸弹
The bomb.

470
00:54:34,500 --> 00:54:39,490
强盗们绑架了公主，留下了她的小表妹
The bandits kidnapped the princess, leaving behind her little nephew.

471
00:54:46,480 --> 00:54:48,970
他们从高山上骑马下山
They rode down from the high mountain deserts

472
00:54:49,050 --> 00:54:50,810
到了他喜爱的地方
to a place he loved.

473
00:54:54,290 --> 00:54:57,350
他跟他孪生兄弟玩耍的地方
He had played as a child with his twin.

474
00:54:59,520 --> 00:55:02,120
就在湖的中央
A palace in the middle of a lake.

475
00:55:43,300 --> 00:55:46,030
那可怜的人怎么了？
What's the matter with that poor fellow?

476
00:55:48,270 --> 00:55:50,570
自从印度人发生了不幸
Ever since the Indian's misfortune

477
00:55:50,640 --> 00:55:53,700
他发誓不再看其他女人
he took a vow to never look at another squaw.

478
00:55:53,780 --> 00:55:57,770
但是男人一旦蒙住脸，就无法显现她的内心所望
But a man cannot show what's in his heart when he hides his face.

479
00:56:00,220 --> 00:56:02,690
谁，请问你是谁？
Who, may I ask, are you?

480
00:56:02,750 --> 00:56:05,810
大家都叫我蒙面侠
To most I am known as the Masked Bandit.

481
00:56:05,890 --> 00:56:08,090
东南方的灾难大侠？
The Scourge of the Southeast?

482
00:56:10,930 --> 00:56:12,450
正是
That's the one.

483
00:56:17,900 --> 00:56:20,500
但也只有我戴上面具才算是
But that's only when I wear the mask.

484
00:56:28,380 --> 00:56:29,850
你是谁？
Who are you?

485
00:56:34,890 --> 00:56:36,350
护士伊芙琳
Nurse Evelyn.

486
00:56:39,390 --> 00:56:44,290
我曾经是伊芙琳、伊芙列丝、伊芙哈特女士，但是我现在就是…
Once I was Lady Evelyn Everest Everhardt, and now I am simply called...

487
00:56:44,800 --> 00:56:47,290
- 伊芙琳姊妹  - 她不是姊妹
- Sister Evelyn.  - She is not a sister.

488
00:56:47,400 --> 00:56:50,460
不，什么？她是的
Bless you. No. What? Yes, she is.

489
00:56:51,470 --> 00:56:54,300
他没有兄弟姊妹
She doesn't have brothers and sisters.

490
00:56:55,310 --> 00:56:58,330
不，她是修女，跟其他修女一样
No, she's a nun, like these nuns out here.

491
00:57:03,010 --> 00:57:05,410
他转向蒙面侠，说…
And she turned from the Masked Bandit, and she said...

492
00:57:05,480 --> 00:57:08,510
- 我可以跟你坦白说吗？ - 当然
- May I be frank with you?  - Of course.

493
00:57:09,420 --> 00:57:12,320
虽然我将我的生命侍奉主
Although I've dedicated my life to God and goodness

494
00:57:12,390 --> 00:57:16,790
我私底下喜欢朝神父丢橘子
I secretly love throwing oranges at our priest.

495
00:57:16,860 --> 00:57:19,350
向左转两个弯，就是厕所
Take two turns to the left and go to the bathroom.

496
00:57:19,430 --> 00:57:20,830
不，你看了我的纸条
No, you read my note.

497
00:57:20,900 --> 00:57:23,270
你说什么，快去厕所？
What are you talking about? Go to the bathroom.

498
00:57:23,330 --> 00:57:25,130
不
No.

499
00:57:25,200 --> 00:57:27,570
那你怎么知道我对神父丢橘子？
How do you know about the priest and the orange?

500
00:57:27,640 --> 00:57:30,110
每个人都知道你喜欢丢神父橘子
Everybody knows you like throwing oranges at the priest.

501
00:57:30,180 --> 00:57:34,340
每个神父都知道，我不是从你那胡言乱语的纸条得到的讯息
Even the priest knows, but I didn't find that out from your gibberish message.

502
00:57:34,410 --> 00:57:36,180
那不是胡言乱语
It's not gibberish.

503
00:58:03,740 --> 00:58:07,140
她想问你，会停留多久
She wants to ask you how much days I have to stay here.

504
00:58:07,210 --> 00:58:10,050
嗯，我要你待到好了为止
Well, I want you to stay here until you get better.

505
00:58:12,550 --> 00:58:15,880
她的石膏几天后就可以拆除
Her cast will come off in a few days

506
00:58:15,950 --> 00:58:20,120
但我要她待到完全康复为止
but I'd like her to stay here until she's completely recovered.

507
00:58:29,270 --> 00:58:32,000
她说我们在这里待太久了
She wants to say that we are spend here too much times

508
00:58:32,070 --> 00:58:33,900
我们必须离开这里
and we have to leave the city.

509
00:58:33,970 --> 00:58:38,200
不，你告诉她，别再果园里工作
No, well, you just tell her that you shouldn't be working in the groves.

510
00:58:38,280 --> 00:58:40,010
那样太危险了
That at your age it's dangerous

511
00:58:40,080 --> 00:58:43,050
你剩下的日子，只要捡水果就好
and you'll spend the rest of your days picking fruit.

512
00:58:43,110 --> 00:58:45,740
否则她会摔下来，一定会摔下来
And then she'll fall. She surely will fall.

513
00:59:12,210 --> 00:59:13,540
谢谢
Thank you.

514
00:59:14,980 --> 00:59:17,710
- 她怎么说？ - 他说好的
- What did she say?  - She says okay.

515
00:59:19,120 --> 00:59:20,550
- 真的？ - 真的
- Really?  - Really.

516
00:59:20,620 --> 00:59:22,640
